        <h1 style="font-size: var(--fs-4xl);">Tamolitch Falls (Blue Pool)</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          One of the most popular and striking natural attractions along the
          McKenzie River in Oregon's Cascade foothills — a place where the
          river vanishes into an ancient lava flow and resurfaces as an
          impossibly blue pool.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <figure class="article-hero">
